Electrcaly isolated interface.

Battery + & - are protected by 1.5A fuses as well as a 50mA PTC fuse
J1 & J2 are protected by a 50mA PTC fuses
Battery side is electrically isolated from the PC side by 4N33 Opto-isolators (5000V isolation voltage)

To prevent incrementing the Dumb charge count when connection to the battery the serial interface must be powered, but the script is not required to be running.
